title: His Own Worst Enemy: The Rise and Fall of Jon Jones  | Part 3

media:group.media:title: His Own Worst Enemy: The Rise and Fall of Jon Jones  | Part 3
media:group.media:description:
In this part of the series, we cover the turbulent years of 2015 and 2016. A period of Jon's career that would be plagued by numerous issues both in and out of the cage. Through this stage of Jon's life, we get a glimpse of what was going to come in the future.
